{"tid":1429455,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[矯情] 雷射革命笑死我 多謝香港人","createTime":"2019-08-07T13:38:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T15:02:36.000Z","uid":267461,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"37361f33aab430d4836ef2ba61f2c11ad95b476f","tid":1429455,"uid":267461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:38:12.000Z","msg":"連續兩個月曠日持久嘅一連串抗爭，又和理非又發夢又睇live，已經令我身心俱疲。<br />\n呢個星期開始覺得自己有焦慮症，好易大笑好易喊又好易情緒失控。<br />\n今日我睇埋警察個記招，我真係嬲到耳仔都痛，放咗工要返去瞓瞓。<br />\n<br />\n一瞓醒睇live, 就見到個太空館藝術品，靚撚到仆街<br />\n<br />\n仲聽到現場有人播羅文激光中去襯托，笑到我仆街。<br />\n未夠，居然有人開live試用雷射筆點煙，點撚咗12分鐘，個人著撚咗，支煙都未著，又笑到仆街。<br />\n<br />\n我開始發現，我地香港人會贏，唔單止因為我地勁，更加係因為我地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有無窮無盡嘅幽默感</span></strong></span><br />\n多謝每一位香港人，總有一日我地會搵返我地美麗嘅香港，就好似今晚嘅太空館一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 雷射革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c4c05a43a1f5dc0dc48e0254c2b63579c9e47f48","tid":1429455,"uid":241774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:42:06.000Z","msg":"香港人創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7640113ce05fcbab59ad0e656c84b11defa48500","tid":1429455,"uid":52727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:42:54.000Z","msg":"多咗好多人買雷射筆，求推Post: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【極重要】請立即停止漫罵及用雷射筆射向拍照的途人/大廈單位<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418134\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418134</a>"},{"pid":"359f3ee2165a712e60b8d0e8b0d4875066c153cf","tid":1429455,"uid":267461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:49:01.000Z","msg":"post吹水台太快沉連自己都搵唔到個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ab19b27b4cf7cf889a4cb99abdb972209fcaac","tid":1429455,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:53:51.000Z","msg":"前線 休息 下 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee3b7b9936151b63e6e592c2d9a266b1cb7e70e","tid":1429455,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:54:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[急] 全港十八區出現武器庫丶軍火原材料</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n汽油彈（英語：Molotov Cocktail，俄語：Кокте́йль Мо́лотова，意為「莫洛托夫雞尾酒」），又稱燃燒彈，是游擊隊等非正規部隊，<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以及街頭暴亂群眾的常用武器，有些罪犯也會以它來縱火。</span></strong></span></ins>軍方亦有採用，不同於制式武器凝固汽油彈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">燃燒瓶的主要構造為：玻璃瓶，</span></span><del><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">瓶內裝有半滿的易燃液體，例如三分之二的汽油與三分之一的油混合而成的液體或酒精（甲醇或乙醇）； 瓶口以軟木塞或塑膠、橡膠、電線膠帶、牛皮膠帶等不透氣塞堵住；瓶口上紮上布塊作引。 使用之前把布塊沾透易燃液體，燃點布塊後把瓶拋出。玻璃瓶撞擊目標破裂，易燃液體傾倒在目標之上，被火點著燃燒，可造成一定的阻絕及殺傷能力。<br />\n<br />\n蘇聯曾經製造制式汽油彈，外面裝有兩根密封有濃硫酸的玻璃管。投擲碰碎之後靠化學反應產生的熱量點燃油料，從而節省了點火步驟。<br />\n<br />\n燃燒瓶的原理跟正規軍隊使用的燃燒彈基本相同；兩者都是以汽油混合使汽油變稠的物料。<br />\n<br />\n另外也有人使用塑膠袋裝汽油，因為塑膠袋可以承載著一定容量的液體。</span></del><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201404/06/P201404040808_photo_1067314.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201404%2F06%2FP201404040808_photo_1067314.JPG&h=2cfe9af1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n18區陸續出現多種以綠色標誌的可疑軍火庫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.enb.gov.hk/sites/default/files/zh-hant/node5045/4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enb.gov.hk%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fzh-hant%2Fnode5045%2F4.jpg&h=eac93a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不知名人士正在提取疑似軍火<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20130401/large/01ls3p2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20130401%2Flarge%2F01ls3p2a.jpg&h=74db3026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201407/20/P201407180904_photo_1071737.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201407%2F20%2FP201407180904_photo_1071737.JPG&h=419e2799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亦有熱心人士幫忙抽走疑似軍火<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.epd.gov.hk/epd/sites/default/files/epd/tc_chi/environmentinhk/waste/eco_responsibility/files/Poster_private1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epd.gov.hk%2Fepd%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fepd%2Ftc_chi%2Fenvironmentinhk%2Fwaste%2Feco_responsibility%2Ffiles%2FPoster_private1.jpg&h=5b1cffb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可疑單張來源不明<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認同請分享 同意請按讚 好人一生平安 <br />\ntag#香港加油!#和平!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"986e95769538d61503a1b958161686ea604a200d","tid":1429455,"uid":267461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:55:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098d161511775b0bd256056715e04c1bebda270c","tid":1429455,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:02:36.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}